    "body": "<span class=\"solution-visible-txt\">All submissions for this problem are available.</span><p>Hey folks, the art department of your college wanted to write words in a parallelogram pattern. Howewer, they want to be able to create it for any word they wish automatically.\n\nYou are required to assist them in doing so by writing a program which satisfies their needs and solves the program. \n\nThe system should output a given word horizontally and multiple times vertically so that each letter in the horizontal word matches the position of that letter vertically.\n\n\n<h3>Input</h3>\n</p><p>The first line should be an integer that represents the number of words that follow.Each word is on a seperate line. All the letters are uppercases and the maximum length of a word is 10.\n\n\n<h3>Output</h3>\n</p><p> The horizontal word is to be in the center of the output.Each vertical word is to read down from the top. The first vertical word uses the first letter of the horizontal word, the last vertical word uses the last letter of the horizontal word. All outputs are to have the same left edge vertically.\n\n\n<h3>Example</h3>\n\n<pre>\n<b>Input:</b>\n2\nTEST\nSAMPLE\n\n\n<b>Output:</b>\nT\n  TE\n TES\nTEST\nEST\nST\nT\n\n     S\n    SA\n   SAM\n  SAMP\n SAMPL\nSAPMLE\nAMPLE\nMPLE\nPLE\nLE\nE\n</pre></p>",
